{"tid":2160030,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點定義低下職業？","createTime":"2020-08-16T16:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T07:50:13.000Z","uid":306528,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"df76c14487b9b3587e229545fca9dae232d6fd66","tid":2160030,"uid":306528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"成日都話職業無分貴賤，即係喺大部份人眼中都認同某啲職業係被認定低下階層先會做。<br />\n<br />\n清潔員、廚師、侍應、保安、地盤工人、的士司機係社會上所謂低下職業，但其實有冇明確原則？<br />\n<br />\n係咪長工時、低人工、低入學門檻就係社會眼中嘅低下職業？<br />\n<br />\n咁點解slash / 創作媒體 又會俾人一種脫俗嘅感覺？明明佢哋生活更加冇保障，更容易隨時失業。<br />\n<br />\n利申絕非歧視，只係唔明點解某啲職業明明唔易做都俾人話係底層"},{"pid":"285f18748f65a44be3bde7c32f4537cd6b648424","tid":2160030,"uid":47658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:53:18.000Z","msg":"低技術果堆囉"},{"pid":"6a4e1f429e631c8b6e7f8958c8aad4e98c95e631","tid":2160030,"uid":78429,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:53:42.000Z","msg":"警察或者政府官員呢啲咪低下"},{"pid":"9335597ffb509fc9bc77771bd1a7d8f2cde68d8a","tid":2160030,"uid":335958,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"警察"},{"pid":"d065710687fb9d5f2df25a865a690034113df8bb","tid":2160030,"uid":207247,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:56:19.000Z","msg":"人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea83ec85e69596b20afec9664c0a2ae3564df976","tid":2160030,"uid":195973,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:58:25.000Z","msg":"職業分腦力同勞力，一般以勞力換錢的都稱為低下職業"},{"pid":"de5b2f59e62b5bfe590d4b17f984aed0aaee9e29","tid":2160030,"uid":354265,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94ae68e9213ef3c6639577d6f2758accfa5a1216","tid":2160030,"uid":50018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:03:40.000Z","msg":"因為slash 比人感覺眼不見為淨或者跟本唔知有佢地存在"},{"pid":"85472dec943832bc3fab5a6eda99c8429d293886","tid