<br />\n<br />\n相反你做example果堆所謂「低下職業」<br />\n就係把口識講野 手識郁 腳識行就已經做得<br />\n我又唔覺得依家睇人工黎分<br />\n家下洗碗做地盤都高人工啦"},{"pid":"25d35fac418bdd457889718a7f9db61a4f751173","tid":2160030,"uid":235021,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a4e1f429e631c8b6e7f8958c8aad4e98c95e631","tid":2160030,"uid":78429,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:53:42.000Z","msg":"警察或者政府官員呢啲咪低下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:34:41.000Z","msg":"現實係社科狗有雄心嘅搶紀侓部隊位（PI IO嗰啲），冇嘅搶低級文職位（ACO CA），連engine 狗都爭住入政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人越大就越想加入建制，唔會好似以前幻想咁以為自己唔會幫政府做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0851b6caa269a91c60b49dbbddcd2d2885175618","tid":2160030,"uid":282930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:37:38.000Z","msg":"驚賊，cold call，的士"},{"pid":"7c445efa63610fa953838e5e8a2e932283040c9b","tid":2160030,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:42:46.000Z","msg":"特首哩份工算唔算賤？人唔賤，坐唔到個位。愈賤愈坐得耐..."},{"pid":"940f496e4c7e51f4509ce9b517ede491aa4251e7","tid":2160030,"uid":6316,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:43:40.000Z","msg":"廚師好撚高尚喎屌你"},{"pid":"e53a33a9c3f0570287fabb53d24527c98da2a95f","tid":2160030,"uid":325200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T00:55:37.000Z","msg":"除左專科<br />\n你街見到既10成有9成都係低下工"}]}